      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity, temperature) documented and traceable to calibrated instrumentation with uncertainty < 5%.",
      "rationale": "Predicate device hemolysis experiments conducted at 37°C, hematocrit 33±1%, viscosity 3.2±0.1 cP. Flow rates measured by Coriolis meter (±0.5%). Rotational speed by optical tachometer (±0.1%). Conditions documented in lab notebook LN-2023-047. Gradation 2 achieved."
