      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single representative geometry evaluated.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require multi-sample geometric variability testing. Single nominal geometry evaluated. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
